* Based on a light novel series by Ishibumi Ichiei with illustrations by Miyama Zero.

Hyoudou Issei, a simple-minded, lecherous second-year high school student is killed
by an innocent-looking beautiful girl on his very first date. Issei is reincarnated
as a devil, with the help of Rias Gremory, and so ends up as her Pawn from then on.
Gremory is not only the president of the Occult Research Club, and the prettiest girl
on campus, but also a high-ranking devil herself.

Are Issei's days without female companionship finally over, or will life after
death turn out to be a lot more complicated than he ever imagined?
